Class CSVStep

  • java.lang.Object

      • com.experian.aperture.datastudio.sdk.step.addons.CSVStep

  • public class CSVStep
extends StepConfiguration
    Custom step that parse CSV file. Used as source input in the StepTestBuilder 
     
 StepTestBuilder.fromCustomStep(executeStep)
                 .withCsvInput(CSV_PATH_INPUT)
                 .build()
                 .execute()
                 .assertWithCsvOutput(CSV_PATH_OUTPUT_VALID)
                 .waitForAssertion();
